#, no-c-format
msgid "2002-01-21"
msgstr "21.1.2002"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<acronym>WebDAV</acronym> is a <emphasis>D</emphasis>istributed <emphasis>A</"
"emphasis>uthoring and <emphasis>V</emphasis>ersioning protocol for the World "
"Wide Web. It allows for easy management of documents and scripts on a &HTTP; "
"server, and has additional features designed to simplify version management "
"amongst multiple authors."
msgstr ""
"<acronym>WebDAV</acronym> pomeni <emphasis>D</emphasis>istributed "
"<emphasis>A</emphasis>uthoring and <emphasis>V</emphasis>ersioning protokol "
"(protokol za deljeno avtorstvo in verzioniranje) za svetovni splet. omogoča "
"enostavno upravljanje dokumentov na &HTTP; strežnikih in ima dodatne "
"funkcije, da več avtorjev lažje upravlja verzije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Usage of this protocol is simple. Type the location you want to view, "
"similar to a &HTTP; &URL; except for the webdav:// protocol name at the "
"start. An example is <userinput>webdav://<replaceable>www.hostname.com/path/"
"</replaceable></userinput>. If you specify a folder name, a list of files "
"and folders will be displayed, and you can manipulate these folders and "
"files just as you would with any other filesystem."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba tega protokola je preprosta. Vpišite lokacijo, ki si jo želite "
"ogledati, podobno kot &HTTP; &URL;, le da napišete ime protokola webdav:// "
"na začetku. Primer: <userinput>webdav://<replaceable>www.ime_gostitelja.com/"
"pot/</replaceable></userinput>. Če želite navesti ime mape, bo izpisan "
"seznam datotek in map. S temi datotekami in mapami lahko upravljate kot z "
"vsakim datotečnim sistemom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "WebDAV Features"
msgstr "WebDAV Lastonsti"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "Locking"
msgstr "Zaklepanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"File locking allows users to lock a file, informing others that they are "
"currently working on this file. This way, editing can be done without fear "
"that the changes may be overwritten by another person who is also editing "
"the same document."
msgstr ""
"Zaklepanje datotek omogoča uporabniku, da zaklene datoteko in s tem obvesti "
"ostale, da trenutno dela na tej datoteki. Tako lahko uporabnik ureja "
"datoteko, brez da bi nekdo drug, ki bi ob istem času urejal isto datoteko, "
"prepisal in pokvaril njegove spremembe."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Source file access"
msgstr "Dostop do izvorne datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<acronym>WebDAV</acronym> allows access to the script which is called to "
"produce a specific page, so changes can be made to the script itself."
msgstr ""
"<acronym>WebDAV</acronym> omogoča dostop do skripte, ki je poklican za "
"izdelavo določene strani, tako da je mogoče spremeniti skripto samo."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Per-document property support"
msgstr "Podpora za lastnosti posameznih dokumentov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Arbitrary properties may be set to assist identification of a document, such "
"as the author."
msgstr ""
"Poljubne lastnosti so lahko nastavljene za lažjo identifikacijo dokumenta, "
"kot npr. avtor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To take advantage of these additional capabilities, you will need an "
"application which supports them. No application currently supports them "
"through this KIO worker."
msgstr ""
"Da bi izkoristili te dodatne zmožnosti, boste potrebovali aplikacijo, ki jih "
"podpira. Trenutno jih nobena aplikacija ne podpira prek tega KIO worker-ja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<acronym>WebDAVS</acronym> is the <acronym>WebDAV</acronym> protocol "
"encrypted via SSL."
msgstr ""
"<acronym>WebDAVS</acronym> je protokol <acronym>WebDAV</acronym> šifriran z "
"SSL."

